# 1.更改标题栏
![avatar][a]
相对路径：_data\navigation.yml
url:\#Biography是"_pages\about.md"中的标签id
```python
main:
  - title: "Home"
    url: \#Biography

  - title: "News"
    url: \#News    
```
# 更改Biography
相对路径："_pages\about.md"
```python
Yongliang Qiao (Member, IEEE) received the B.S. degree in electrical engineering and automation and the M.S. degree in agricultural electriﬁcation and automation from Northwest A&F University, Xianyang, China, and the Ph.D. degree in computer science from the University of Technology of Belfort-Montbéliard, Belfort, France. He was a Research Associate with the Australian Centre for Field Robotics, University of Sydney, Australia. His research interests include smart farming, agricultural robots, deep learning, multi-sensor fusion, and intelligent perception.
```

# 更改Publications
![avatar][d]
## 填写文章内容
文章内容的相对路径："markdown_generator\publications.tsv"
使用excel打开tsv文件
```python
pub_date	title	venue	excerpt	citation	url_slug	paper_url
只需要填入title和citation中的内容， 其他的复制下来
```
## 生成html文件
代码相对路径："markdown_generator\publications.py"
生成文件的相对路径："_publications"
**注意代码生成后看一下生成的md文件，不要有非utf-8之外的字符**

==显示index.html：==
"_pages\about.md"
```python
<span id="Publications" class="section-subheading">Publications</span>
  <ul>
  {% for post in site.publications reversed %}
    {% include archive-single-cv.html %}
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
```
about.md中使用的html的相对路径："_includes\archive-single-cv.html"

# Talks and presentations
![avatar][e]
## 填写文章内容
文章内容的相对路径："markdown_generator\talks.tsv"
使用excel打开tsv文件
```python
title	type	url_slug	venue	date	location	talk_url	description
```
## 生成html文件
代码相对路径："markdown_generator\talks.py"
生成文件的相对路径："_talks"
**注意代码生成后看一下生成的md文件，不要有非utf-8之外的字符**

==显示index.html：==
"_pages\about.md"
```python
<span id="Talks" class="section-subheading">Talks and presentations</span>
  <ul>
  {% for post in site.talks reversed %}
    {% include archive-single-talk.html %}
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
```
about.md中使用的html的相对路径："_includes\archive-single-talk.html"

# Patent
## 填写文章内容
文章内容的相对路径："markdown_generator\Patent.tsv"
使用excel打开tsv文件
```python
title
```
注意：title中需要有". Patent No.:ZL202222670720.1"

## 生成html文件
代码相对路径："markdown_generator\Patent.py"
生成文件的相对路径："_patent"
**注意代码生成后看一下生成的md文件，不要有非utf-8之外的字符**

==显示index.html：==
"_pages\about.md"
```python
<span id="Patent" class="section-subheading">Patent</span>
  <ul>
  {% for post in site.patent reversed %}
    {% include archive-single-patent.html %}
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
```
about.md中使用的html的相对路径："_includes\archive-single-patent.html"
